including low and high level protocols!  I'd be the first to say
it would be a Bad Idea for exactly the reasons you cite.  I would
also add that separation is critical because different
applications may need different high level protocols.  SGML works
great for publishing type applications, but it certainly is not
an answer to every text processing applications. 

-john

