	by fallout.campusview.indiana.edu (8.8.5/8.8.5) with SMTP id QAA04102;
	Wed, 28 May 1997 16:14:11 -0500 (EST)
Date: Wed, 28 May 1997 16:14:10 -0500 (EST)
From: John Fieber <jfieber@indiana.edu>
