    Walt> Perhaps this is a legacy of too much emphasis on legibility of plain
    Walt> text.  The world has progessed. HTML mail really is better than
    Walt> plain text mail.  Yes, there are systems and mail handlers that
    Walt> can't cope but if you keep singing the plain text mantra they will
